      <hr /><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1><span>672</span> - <span>Title Related to the Entity</span><span> (R)</span></h1>
      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Authority - full</div>
      <div class="datename">April 2013</div>
      <hr />
      <table width="100%" class="indicators">
